{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Shaida Badiee is a co-founder and managing director of "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://opendatawatch.com/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Open Data Watch"}]},{"type":"text","value":", an NGO focused on monitoring and promoting open data in national statistical offices. She has been an active member of the UN Secretary General’s advisory group on data revolution, co-chairs the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"http://unsdsn.org/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sustainable Development Solutions Network (SDSN)"}]},{"type":"text","value":", and has played a key role with the startup of the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"http://www.data4sdgs.org/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Global Partnership for Sustainable Development Data"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ms Badiee brings several decades of experience in managing global development statistics as the long-time Director of the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://data.worldbank.org/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"World Bank’s Development Data Group"}]},{"type":"text","value":". During her tenure, flagship global statistical products were launched such as the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://data.worldbank.org/products/wdi"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"World Development Indicators"}]},{"type":"text","value":", Global Development Finance, and the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://elibrary.worldbank.org/doi/book/10.1596/978-0-8213-9757-2"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Atlas of Global Development"}]},{"type":"text","value":". In 2010, she led the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://data.worldbank.org/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"World Bank’s Open Data Initiative"}]},{"type":"text","value":", a ground-breaking program to provide full and free access to the World Bank’s extensive statistical databases."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Prior to that, she played a key role in the creation and operation of "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"http://www.paris21.org/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"PARIS21"}]},{"type":"text","value":" as well as leading international efforts to coordinate technical and financial support for statistics through initiatives like the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"http://www.worldbank.org/en/data/statistical-capacity-building/marrakech-action-plan-for-statistics"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Marrakech Action Plan for Statistics"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]}],"data":{"quirksMode":false}},"frontmatter":{"firstName":"Shaida","lastName":"Badiee","committee":true}},"imageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/shaida-badiee-d35cf6335618059a4f177fccc39ad415-30c8e.jpg"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"shaida-badiee"}}